{
  "stem": "27507.10",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as soon as it was light in the morning, as soon as the curfew was over-- I think at 5:00 o'clock in the morning or something like that-- I went down.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I manage-- I think I caught a-- again, jumped on a tram, and came to the place where-- where we lived in [NON-ENGLISH], came to the house.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the gate, in this typical Polish entrance, a Warsaw entrance hole, I met my mother, who was running out of there, out of her mind with red eyes, crying, terribly upset, because she was, of course, sure that since I didn't appear there for the night that I was now already gone, and dead, and finished.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And probably, she heard some shooting during the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she thought that it was the Gestapo who caught me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they all-- they were certain that that was the end of me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she-- now, suddenly, I appeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she was overjoyed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But on the other hand, Miss [NON-ENGLISH], who kept us, thought that really was-- she was afraid once too more-- once too much-- or-- or too strongly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she told us that, unfortunately, we have to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had no choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We left there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to look for another place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- I don't know how my mother exactly looked for those places, who exactly gave her this place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went to that place into some room, or flat, of some of the house-- how to say the porter of the house in the old town of Warsaw in Pivna.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But once we came there in the afternoon, we somehow had the feeling that people were after us, that somebody is blackmailing us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, indeed, somebody came and demanded money.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
